{"tid":2392740,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"你down咗iOS 14.5未？戴口罩可用 Face ID，解決5G雙SIM問題","createTime":"2021-02-03T03:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T05:33:56.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7db33437c8872b6e14d3ca6a238fac4b54657b","tid":2392740,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"iPhone 戴口罩都可用 Face ID？ 升上 iOS 14.5 配 Apple Watch 就得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_01_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_01_1024.JPG&h=2ace31c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple 剛剛為 iPhone 預告了個大升級，只要 iPhone 系統升級到 iOS 14.5，即使戴著口罩，將口鼻遮蓋，只要配合 Apple Watch 亦可以用 Face ID 解鎖，解決疫情下使用 iPhone 常見的問題。另外，iOS 14.5 下亦啟動了雙 5G 網絡功能，絕對不容錯過。<br />\n<br />\niOS 14.5 即將推出<br />\n戴口罩亦可用 Face ID 解鎖<br />\n支援雙 5G 網絡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_02_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_02_600.jpeg&h=a1e4a082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niOS 14.5 Developer Beta 1 登場。<br />\n於疫情下，人人日日戴口罩，讓 iPhone 的 Face ID 沒法提供有效的電話解鎖功能，為習慣使用 Face ID 的用家帶來不便。但 Apple 剛剛推出 iOS 14.5 開發者 Beta 測試版，預告 iPhone 只要升級到 iOS 14.5 版本，便可以解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_03_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_03_600.jpeg&h=7c727907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下載及安裝描述檔，就可以找到 iOS 14.5 Developer Beta 升級檔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_04_600.jpg&h=4cfb2719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要用新功能，用戶需要將 Apple Watch 升級至 WatchOS 7.4 Developer Beta"},{"pid":"9388485de5bc3637abb7de48f86cf8ae0267b26e","tid":2392740,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"Update 01：戴口罩用 Face ID <br />\n<br />\n當 iPhone 系統為 iOS 14.5 時，只要手上戴上解鎖的 Apple Watch，便可以如常在已配對的 iPhone 上，以 Face ID 進行解鎖。當解鎖成功時，Apple Watch 亦會震動及作出提示。使用方法如下（按圖睇 step by step 教學）：<br />\n<br />\n即使舊錶，亦可利用此功能解鎖 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是這功能巧妙利用 iPhone 用家會配戴 Apple watch 及 iPhone 不離手的概念來進行。意味若你戴上 Apple Watch 時，有其他人拿起你的手機解鎖，只要 處解鎖狀態下的 Appel Watch 與  iPhone 有足夠近距離（實試一間房兩角依然成功）亦可以解鎖 。不過成功解鎖時，Apple watch 會震動提示，並提供即時  Lock 機選項，用作最後的保安手段。<br />\n<br />\nUpdate 02：雙 5G <br />\n<br />\n過往 iPhone 12 在雙 SIM下，未能使用 5G 網絡，但升級後問題便迎刃而解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_09_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_09_600.jpeg&h=462d1f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雙卡雙待時，可使用 5G 網絡。<br />\nUpdate 03：自訂 App 追蹤項目<br />\n<br />\n開發者必須先獲得你的同意，方可追蹤你。你可在「設定」中，查看已授權哪些 app 可進行追蹤並更改設定。私隱保護更全面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_12_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_12_600.jpeg&h=3ceb41f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更全面的「追蹤」設定功能，照顧用戶的私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_13_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_13_600.jpeg&h=e17d9871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於「設定」-》「私隱」-》「追蹤」可以詳細設置。<br />\nUpdate 04：Siri 致電緊急聯絡人<br />\n<br />\n只要在「健康」內設置緊急聯絡人，便可以利用 SIRI 要求撥打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_10_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_10_600.jpeg&h=5cb7f4bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可透過 Siri，撥打緊急聯絡人電話。<br />\nUpdate 05：遊戲手掣支援<br />\n<br />\n不論是 PS5 或 Xbox X 新手製，均可與 iOS 14.5 下的 iPhone 進行配對。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2865000/2869094/20210202_AIR_11_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2865000%2F2869094%2F20210202_AIR_11_600.jpeg&h=81212d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niOS 14.5 下，支援新 Console 手掣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2869094?=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2869094%3F%3D&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=920a9db0\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2869094?=</a>"},{"pid":"fc895c2e976ff42d0cfa62bb7411cb598a50e4ea","tid":2392740,"uid":73092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"等正式版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998c9beb0201e5ff05b331a68ad388ca815667e0","tid":2392740,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"14.4上一陣連登都熱到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea44c97752050a7235c190222573843615033a24","tid":2392740,"uid":38301,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個只係第一個 developer beta<br />\n就算好急住想玩都等第一個 public beta 啦"}]}